com.gridgraph.graphcore

Interface IQueryBuilder


  • public interface IQueryBuilder
    We need something like this class to provide an iterative query like interface.
    Examples: IQueryBuilder builder = IQueryBuilderFactory.createBuilder(); Iterator<Vertex> vertices = builder.schemas("person", "software") .direction(Direction.BOTH) .has('age', gt(30)) .vertices();
    Author:
    guobao.chen
